pik Ini","value":"tentang-topik-ini","line":15,"column":0,"depth":2},"entry-point--mulai-dari-sini":{"type":"header","text":"Entry Point — Mulai dari Sini","value":"entry-point--mulai-dari-sini","line":23,"column":0,"depth":2},"klaster-gagasan":{"type":"header","text":"Klaster Gagasan","value":"klaster-gagasan","line":30,"column":0,"depth":2},"mengapa-sistem-eksternal-diperlukan":{"type":"header","text":"Mengapa Sistem Eksternal Diperlukan","value":"mengapa-sistem-eksternal-diperlukan","line":32,"column":0,"depth":3},"prinsip-kerja-sistem-yang-efektif":{"type":"header","text":"Prinsip Kerja Sistem yang Efektif","value":"prinsip-kerja-sistem-yang-efektif","line":37,"column":0,"depth":3},"akan-berkembang-saat-zettel-baru-ditambahkan":{"type":"header","text":"(Akan berkembang saat Zettel baru ditambahkan)","value":"akan-berkembang-saat-zettel-baru-ditambahkan","line":41,"column":0,"depth":3},"sumber-utama":{"type":"header","text":"Sumber Utama","value":"sumber-utama","line":49,"column":0,"depth":2},"pertanyaan-terbuka":{"type":"header","text":"Pertanyaan Terbuka","value":"pertanyaan-terbuka","line":54,"column":0,"depth":2},"moc-terkait":{"type":"header","text":"MOC Terkait","value":"moc-terkait","line":60,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"6ie1ckeu7jfftzq54vt9e44","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"moc-personal-knowledge-management\">MOC: Personal Knowledge Management<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#moc-personal-knowledge-management\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"tentang-topik-ini\">Tentang Topik Ini<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tentang-topik-ini\"></a></h2>\n<p>Personal Knowledge Management (PKM) adalah praktik mengelola informasi dan pengetahuan yang kamu kumpulkan secara personal — bukan untuk organisasi, tapi untuk pertumbuhan dan produktivitas pribadimu.</p>\n<p>Topik ini mencakup: bagaimana belajar lebih efektif, bagaimana menyimpan dan menemukan kembali pengetahuan, dan bagaimana mengubah informasi menjadi output nyata (tulisan, keputusan, keahlian).</p>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"entry-point--mulai-dari-sini\">Entry Point — Mulai dari Sini<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#entry-point--mulai-dari-sini\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.202604170003\">Koneksi antar gagasan lebih bernilai dari koleksi informasi</a> — <strong>Koneksi > Koleksi</strong>: prinsip paling fundamental yang membedakan PKM yang efektif dari tumpukan catatan</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.202604170001\">Second brain memperluas kapasitas berpikir dengan memindahkan beban memori ke sistem eksternal</a> — <strong>Otak sebagai prosesor, bukan storage</strong>: mengapa kita butuh sistem eksternal</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"klaster-gagasan\">Klaster Gagasan<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#klaster-gagasan\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"mengapa-sistem-eksternal-diperlukan\">Mengapa Sistem Eksternal Diperlukan<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#mengapa-sistem-eksternal-diperlukan\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.202604170001\">Second brain memperluas kapasitas berpikir dengan memindahkan beban memori ke sistem eksternal</a> — Second brain memperluas kapasitas berpikir dengan offloading memori</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.202604170002\">Ide yang tidak ditulis sama dengan ide yang tidak ada</a> — Ide yang tidak ditulis sama dengan ide yang tidak ada</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"prinsip-kerja-sistem-yang-efektif\">Prinsip Kerja Sistem yang Efektif<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#prinsip-kerja-sistem-yang-efektif\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.202604170003\">Koneksi antar gagasan lebih bernilai dari koleksi informasi</a> — Koneksi antar gagasan lebih bernilai dari koleksi informasi</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"akan-berkembang-saat-zettel-baru-ditambahkan\"><em>(Akan berkembang saat Zettel baru ditambahkan)</em><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#akan-berkembang-saat-zettel-baru-ditambahkan\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code>zettel.YYYYMMDDHHMMSS</code> — Atomicity: satu catatan = satu gagasan</li>\n<li><code>zettel.YYYYMMDDHHMMSS</code> — Mengapa kita harus menulis dengan kata sendiri</li>\n<li><code>zettel.YYYYMMDDHHMMSS</code> — Structure notes sebagai peta navigasi</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"sumber-utama\">Sumber Utama<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#sumber-utama\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.literature.building-a-second-brain\">Literature Note — Building a Second Brain</a> — Building a Second Brain (Tiago Forte, 2022)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/book-summaries.building-a-second-brain\">Building a Second Brain</a> — ringkasan awal sebelum diproses ke Zettel</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"pertanyaan-terbuka\">Pertanyaan Terbuka<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#pertanyaan-terbuka\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Bagaimana PKM berinteraksi dengan <em>project management</em> harian? Kapan sesuatu masuk ke Zettel vs task list?</li>\n<li>Apakah ada titik di mana sistem PKM menjadi terlalu kompleks dan kontraproduktif?</li>\n<li>Bagaimana mengintegrasikan Zettelkasten dengan proses belajar coding (TIL)?</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"moc-terkait\">MOC Terkait<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#moc-terkait\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">zettel.moc.writing (Private)</a> <em>(belum dibuat)</em> — PKM dan writing saling mendukung</li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">zettel.moc.learning-systems (Private)</a> <em>(belum dibuat)</em> — spaced repetition, deliberate practice</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a class=\"color-tag\" style=\"--tag-color: #f8481c;\" href=\"/sotoy/notes/tags.structure-note\">structure-note</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"color-tag\" style=\"--tag-color: #edc8ff;\" href=\"/sotoy/notes/tags.moc\">moc</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"color-tag\" style=\"--tag-color: #f0944d;\" href=\"/sotoy/notes/tags.knowledge-management\">knowledge-management</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"color-tag\" style=\"--tag-color: #de9dac;\" href=\"/sotoy/notes/tags.zettelkasten\">zettelkasten</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/notes.zettelkasten\">Zettelkasten di Dendron — Panduan Implementasi</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/notes.zettelkasten.cara-pakai\">Cara Pakai Zettelkasten di Project Ini</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.software-architecture\">MOC: Software Architecture</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"dendronVersion":"0.83.0","vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"","dateFormat":"","addBehavior":"childOfCurrent","statusSymbols":{"":" ","wip":"w","done":"x","assigned":"a","moved":"m","blocked":"b","delegated":"l","dropped":"d","pending":"y"},"prioritySymbols":{"H":"high","M":"medium","L":"low"},"todoIntegration":false,"createTaskSelectionType":"selection2link","taskCompleteStatus":["done","x"]},"graph":{"zoomSpeed":1,"createStub":false},"enableAutoCreateOnDefinition":false,"enableXVaultWikiLink":false,"enableRemoteVaultInit":true,"enableUserTags":true,"enableHashTags":true,"workspaceVaultSyncMode":"noCommit","enableAutoFoldFrontmatter":false,"enableEditorDecorations":true,"maxPreviewsCached":10,"maxNoteLength":204800,"s